      "name": "Commission the UPS Loop",
      "description": "Close SW_Mains to energise the circuit. PS1 will power LOAD1 directly through the splitter (SPL1) and Junction JNC1. At the same time, the splitter feeds the lower path: AC passes through Rectifier REC1, converting it to DC (red wires), which charges Battery1. Win when LOAD1 is active and the battery is charging.",
